title: It really is that easy! Pending in Austin. 1 Beds, 1 Baths
posting_body: ['Tour this lovely studio apartment in the Escala Community, Austin TX!', 'Located in the heart of the west campus at 26th and San Gabriel, just a three blocks from the University of Texas.', 'Fall in love with the open floorplan with a fully equipped kitchen boasting stainless steel appliances and built-in features such as bookshelves and a fireplace.', 'The home has a walk-in closet and a full bathroom with single vanity, cabinets and a bathtub to relax after a long day!', 'Community amenities include the inner courtyard with a beautiful pool to be enjoyed on the hot summer days, along with a reserved parking space.', 'Tour and apply to this one before it’s gone!', '**', 'In person tours required', '**', 'All renters are enrolled in the resident benefits package.', ' ***', 'Send Text Message FEDERICO to', '--to set up a viewing--', 'Call/Text/Email ANYTIME!', 'Federico Argueta', 'show contact info', '(ask for ID# 6242359)', 'All City Real Estate Company', 'Have other properties available....', '(Houses, Duplexes, Apartments, Condos, All Areas)', 'Please be Aware of SCAMS...', 'Do NOT reply to this ad, please call/text for a fast response.', 'Listed By: Benjamin Doherty, Sunroom Rentals Texas, LLC']
